Reversing number without loop
a=234
b=a%10
c=0
c=c*10+b
a//=10
b=a%10
c=c*10+b
a//=10
b=a%10
c=c*10+b
print(c)

Reversing number with loop
a=234
c=0
while a!=0:
    b=a%10
    c=c*10+b
    a//=10
print(c)

